metadata.Summary: This frame shows the n8n workflow editor, with a 'Save output changes before closing?' modal window overlaid on the 'Save to Airtable' node configuration panel. The user is prompted to either 'Discard' or 'Save' the changes made to the 'Save to Airtable' node before closing its configuration. The 'You have control' message from OpenAI's Operator remains at the bottom.
